    SOURCE MATERIAL ANALYSIS & PLAN:
    1. Narrative: Move from defining the concept to actionable pillars, then the specific tool (Hunger Scale), process (Mindfulness), and finally the results.
    2. Visualizations Choices:
       - Pillars: Bar Chart to contrast "Intuitive" vs "Diet" mentality (Goal: Compare).
       - Permission: Pie Chart to show the shift in mental energy (Goal: Inform/Composition).
       - Hunger Scale: Horizontal Bar Chart to visualize the 1-10 spectrum (Goal: Organize/Measure).
       - Mindfulness: HTML/CSS Flowchart blocks (Goal: Process/Organize) - STRICTLY NO SVG/MERMAID.
       - Benefits: Line Chart for anxiety trends (Goal: Change over time) and Radar Chart for holistic comparison (Goal: Compare attributes).
    3. Palette: "Fresh & Balanced" - #2ecc71 (Green), #3498db (Blue), #f39c12 (Orange), #e74c3c (Red).
    4. Compliance: NO SVG, NO Mermaid. Canvas used. Text wrapping logic in JS.
